{
  "texts": [
    "The accuracy of tissue detection and polyp classification was determined using pathologist-driven consensus diagnoses as the gold standard.",
    "All microscopic diagnoses and additional descriptions generated by GPT-4 were further assessed by pathologists.",
    "The mean diagnostic scores for GPT-4 and each pathologist were calculated as provided.",
    "Parametric tests were employed to compare GPT-4's performance at different time points.",
    "To assess the reliability of GPT-4's performance, Cohen's Kappa coefficient and Intraclass Correlation (ICC) were utilized."
  ]
}